Set criteria for Favorable/Unfavorable effects. We followed the “General Guidelines for Methodologies on Research and Evaluation of Traditional Medicine-World Health Organization” for clinical evidence (
   WHO, 2000) (

    Table 1
   ). We agreed on six key criteria for safety (

